  "kind": "Theorem",
  "title": "Associativity of Union and Intersection",
  "root": "",
  "statement": "Let $A,B,C$ be sets. Then\n\\[\n(A \\cup B) \\cup C = A \\cup (B \\cup C)\n\\quad\\text{and}\\quad\n(A \\cap B) \\cap C = A \\cap (B \\cap C).\n\\]",
